            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> Iuno<lb break="no" n="2"/>ni Reginae <lb n="3"/>Mercurio et <lb n="4"/>Genio loci <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Paternus b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> Vero III <lb n="7"/>et Quadrato co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1: O klein am Zeilenende; Z. 3: ME-Ligatur; Z. 5: BF-Ligatur mit mittig durchgezogener Querhaste; O klein zwischen C und S. Auf der linken Nebenseite stilisiertes Blitzbündel, auf der rechten Nebenseite Opfermesser und Axt.</p>
            </div>
